  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/cedfe7f184fb29c17f3e0839309fefb3.poster.avif?t=1726463955\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/cedfe7f184fb29c17f3e0839309fefb3.webm?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/cedfe7f184fb29c17f3e0839309fefb3.mp4?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join Rose and Kirk in this head-breaking Cube Adventure and prove that you are a true Cube Raider.<br>Cube Raiders offers gamers four different game modes for one or two players.<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/fca2c9ffb21f7f4383e2667b3782ddb4.poster.avif?t=1726463955\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/fca2c9ffb21f7f4383e2667b3782ddb4.webm?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/fca2c9ffb21f7f4383e2667b3782ddb4.mp4?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Face the dangers and surprises in each temple and solve more than 99 puzzles for just one player.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/d8ab2e373ca76af69fd6a3d19c3e9e47.poster.avif?t=1726463955\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/d8ab2e373ca76af69fd6a3d19c3e9e47.webm?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/d8ab2e373ca76af69fd6a3d19c3e9e47.mp4?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Have fun together and play a joint adventure with more than 59 puzzles created for two players.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/1989034b8153abe34fa669697a53c26c.poster.avif?t=1726463955\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/1989034b8153abe34fa669697a53c26c.webm?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/1989034b8153abe34fa669697a53c26c.mp4?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get the highest score in \"Endless\" mode before time runs out or the entire floor gets filled with dice!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/954fc032f792b6152d56df3362fc638e.poster.avif?t=1726463955\" width=600 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/954fc032f792b6152d56df3362fc638e.webm?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373240/extras/954fc032f792b6152d56df3362fc638e.mp4?t=1726463955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Put companionship aside and show who the best Cube Raider is in the \"Duel\" mode.",
